{"tid":1672770,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(回帶 mon post狗睇路) 休班警疑刺激鄰居 遭刺8刀劏肚露腸","createTime":"2019-10-24T09:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T13:23:37.000Z","uid":222970,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1cc330ff63b7141ca675270ef23e6ba136f5f87a","tid":1672770,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"休班警疑刺激鄰居　遭刺8刀劏肚露腸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cbMZv6L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcbMZv6L.jpg&h=273ed9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年今日，2017年10月24日，《蘋果日報》報道了一名休班警疑觸怒鄰居，被利刀襲擊重傷的案件。<br />\n<br />\n該名休班警名叫吳超雄（當年49歲），據了解當時吳到葵涌安蔭邨是要探望母親，在拉開鐵閘準備入屋之際，住對面的姓楊疑兇突然從後撲出，揮刀施襲，更意圖將對方推入自己屋內。<br />\n<br />\n而在走廊糾纏期間，吳雖作出反抗但依然受傷，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">右腹等多處中刀，肚皮更被割開一5厘米傷口露出腸臟。</span></strong></span>吳最後擺脫對方，逃跑到5至6個樓層下的後樓梯，其間更因仆倒令左手骨折。<br />\n<br />\n未幾警方接報到場，將疑兇制服和以涉嫌傷人罪名將他拘捕。吳隨即被送院搶救，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>經醫生診斷後，身上共有8處刀傷，除腹部的5厘米傷口外，頸部傷口亦達14厘米，肺部及橫膈膜亦被刺穿，情況嚴重。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有街坊表示姓楊疑兇和受襲的休班警也曾經是鄰居，大家早在20多年前便是梨木樹邨14座的左鄰右里，直至屋邨清拆被安排搬遷至安蔭邨打對面的單位。究竟是甚麼原因令相處多年、相安無事的隔籬鄰舍衍生出一單血腥傷人案？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Mon post狗睇路 <br />\n凡事唔好做到太盡 逼人走上絕路 否則後果自負<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1afd82b55138aca4fc14c2300158fe66ed4bc5ae","tid":1672770,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oxkjwiy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOxkjwiy.gif&h=7747fc61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5aa91e89ab0fd7e74472eef620a7805f50c1f4a0","tid":1672770,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xmgrbiD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxmgrbiD.gif&h=de0463d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MVWyw4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MVWyw4.gif&h=f462841e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ibR6R5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ibR6R5.gif&h=17af7e6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90023084a33561f4c69a246966db8dbec15d389e","tid":1672770,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab722e6630249d62187779ac1ffa53bbc57c946","tid":1672770,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6ca65141dad200f5c98ce1e23de5255955cfd8","tid":1672770,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"請阿sir 入黎睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警</strong>犯咗死罪</span>，已<span style=\"color: red;\">大禍臨頭</span>！<br />\n+ <span style=\"color: gold;\">送條妙計<strong>俾科士解圍</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671833\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671833</a>"},{"pid":"8d9f661a5ef6bccdb4cb4e3cabd87f97f7beff04","tid":1672770,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:58:11.000Z","msg":"已經有隻mon post狗負皮左"},{"pid":"5c67045487f3ce7697590bd3c8e19fa38fbe832a","tid":1672770,"uid":8007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:03:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20180817/s00001/1534478665845/%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%AA%8D%E5%88%80%E5%88%BA%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6-%E5%88%A46%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E9%86%AB%E